OL,3,CWales great George North to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby at end of season
OL,6,FWales great George North has announced
OL,7,Fhe will retire from rugby at the end
OL,8,Fof the season.
OL,10,FThe 34-year-old began his career with
OL,11,FScarlets and joined Northampton Saints
OL,12,Fin 2013, where he won the Premiership.
OL,14,FThe wing or centre made the move to
OL,15,FOspreys in 2018, spending five years
OL,16,Fthere before joining French side
OL,17,FProvence.
