OL,3,CWales great George North to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby at end of season
OL,6,FNorth retired from international rugby
OL,7,Fin 2024 with 121 caps for Wales and
OL,8,Ftoured twice with the British and
OL,9,FIrish Lions during his career.
OL,11,FIn a video posted on X, North said:
OL,12,F"Hi guys, I just want to come on here
OL,13,Fand let you know at the end of the
OL,14,Fseason I'll be retiring.
OL,16,F"For me, it's the right time. I've
OL,17,Fbeen able to live out my childhood
OL,18,Fdream for many seasons playing with
OL,19,Fsome of the best players, coaches and
OL,20,Fthe staff behind.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU
