CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777453578
OL,3,CWales great George North to retire
OL,4,Cfrom rugby at end of season
OL,6,F"I can't thank my family, my friends
OL,7,Fand you guys enough for the support
OL,8,Fyou've shown me over the years.
OL,10,F"Honestly it's meant the world to me.
OL,11,FThe next chapter? Still working on
OL,12,Fthat one, but I'm excited to see where
OL,13,Fthat journey takes me.
OL,15,F"So again, from the bottom of my
OL,16,Fheart, thank you. Diolch."
